burlap.domain.singleagent.mountaincar

Class MCRandomStateGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • burlap.domain.singleagent.mountaincar.MCRandomStateGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StateGenerator

    public class MCRandomStateGenerator
extends Object
implements StateGenerator
    Generates MountainCar states with the x-position between some specified range and the velocity between some specified range. By default, the ranges are the full ranges supported by the domain, but they can be individually changed.
    Author:
    James MacGlashan
